text: Ashu Malik (born 6 April 1983) is an Indian politician from the Indian state of Uttar Pradesh. He is a member of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Council. He is also a member of the Samajwadi Party in Uttar Pradesh. == References == Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Samajwadi Party politicians from Uttar Pradesh Category:Members of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Council Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
